        <RegExpr attribute="Branch Instruction" context="CheckCondition" String="\b(?:B|BL|BLX|BX|TBB|TBH)(?:EQ|NE|CS|HS|CC|LO|MI|PL|VS|VC|HI|LS|GE|LT|GT|LE|AL)?\b(?=\s|$)" insensitive="true" />
